                  </div>
                  <span class="">唐晓峰《走在大潮边上》
《鬼见愁战歌》之简谱

</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-01-24 01:38</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                唐晓峰《走在大潮边上》<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>《鬼见愁战歌》之简谱
<div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p41386710-1.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>

                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/41386710/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2017-01-24 01:38
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="41386661">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/51097623/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u51097623-2.jpg" alt="喜乐" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
